---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import PetitionSection from '../components/PetitionSection.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Clemency & Public Support">
  <h1>Clemency & Public Support</h1>

  <p>
    Brian Zater has submitted a formal clemency petition seeking a sentence reduction
    based on demonstrated rehabilitation, institutional conduct, and documented contributions
    over more than two decades of incarceration.
  </p>

  <p>
    This page provides an overview of the petition, supporting materials, and ways to
    express public support. Your signature on the Change.org petition or a formal
    statement of support helps demonstrate the breadth of belief in second chances and
    evidence-based sentencing reform.
  </p>

  <p>
    The petition outlines the legal foundation, personal development, institutional
    record, and community support surrounding this request. All materials are available
    for review.
  </p>

  <PetitionSection />
</MainLayout>
